1
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Day two of the class trip...</font>

2
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Group activities!</font>

3
00:00:12,420 --> 00:00:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't the fall leaves
and the gardens pretty?</font>

4
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fall colors were nice...</font>

5
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the timing didn't work out, did it?</font>

6
00:00:19,670 --> 00:00:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? T-Timing for what?</font>

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're pretending you don't know?</font>

8
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going the same places as him, right?</font>

9
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, that's...</font>

10
00:00:27,710 --> 00:00:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just a "maybe we might
see each other."</font>

11
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being able to take beautiful photos
is enough to make me than happy.</font>

12
00:00:35,750 --> 00:00:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Truthfully, I was just a little hopeful.</i></font>

13
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, instead of going "it would be
nice if we saw each other,"</font>

14
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you could just set a time
and place to meet.</font>

15
00:00:45,830 --> 00:00:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

16
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Be alone with him somewhere</i>
<i>other than school?</i></font>

17
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could never.</i></font>

18
00:00:53,330 --> 00:00:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but... Hon-chan, leaving you
alone so suddenly would be...</font>

19
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? That's your reason? Really?</font>

20
00:01:02,630 --> 00:01:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. That was an underhanded excuse.</font>

21
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. You're forgiven.</font>

22
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate people who are evasive about
their true feelings, you know?</font>

23
00:01:11,380 --> 00:01:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry.</font>

24
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, girls! What are
you two talking about?</font>

25
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing!</font>

26
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? She lied.</i></font>

27
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES</font>

28
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LOVE FORTUNE TELLING STONE</font>

29
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stones say if your love is real!</font>

30
00:02:58,880 --> 00:02:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, how lovely.</font>

31
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you close your eyes and manage
to walk from one stone to the other,</font>

32
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your love will be fulfilled!</font>

33
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

34
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, it'd be too cringe to do, right?</i></font>

35
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, me! I'll do it!</font>

36
00:03:11,290 --> 00:03:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

37
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it, Yamada Man!</font>

38
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go! Go!</font>

39
00:03:20,380 --> 00:03:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Yamada Man!
- Yamada's doing it.</font>

40
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

41
00:03:24,380 --> 00:03:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Left!</font>

42
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reft!</font>

43
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which way?!</font>

44
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice fight!</font>

45
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy your love will work out.</font>

46
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morimo!</font>

47
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?
Don't get in the way!</font>

48
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no.</font>

49
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm way bigger than the stone, so the
effectiveness should be greater.</font>

50
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What logic is that?</font>

51
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! I see a bunch of
our uniforms over there.</font>

52
00:03:53,210 --> 00:03:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that group 7?</font>

53
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try talking to him.</font>

54
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

55
00:03:57,750 --> 00:04:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he's with his friends.</font>

56
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be interrupting.</font>

57
00:04:02,380 --> 00:04:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if you're all right with that,
then I guess it's fine, but...</font>

58
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! Look over here!</font>

59
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that, Tani. Smile!</font>

60
00:04:11,210 --> 00:04:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why make a face
like that for the camera?</font>

61
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! Look this way! Smile! Smile!</font>

62
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we little kids?</font>

63
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki, your face is tense.</font>

64
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki! Your face is weird!</font>

65
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My face is weird?!</font>

66
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and take it.</font>

67
00:04:24,290 --> 00:04:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your feelings showed!</font>

68
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Looking good!</font>

69
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Going on your class trip with
a girlfriend must be nice, right?</font>

70
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

71
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I had one, I'd never</i>
<i>want to be that open about it.</i></font>

72
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LOVE</font>

73
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just bought an charm,
so I have high hopes for future me!</font>

74
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Hey, that's no fair!</font>

75
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And after you got in my way!</font>

76
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if there's a charm that—</font>

77
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada-kun.</font>

78
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um, I'm sorry for interrupting
so suddenly. I saw you, so...</font>

79
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GIGGLE GIGGLE</font>

80
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... thought I'd try
speaking to you. That's all.</font>

81
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Voom!</font>

82
00:05:11,170 --> 00:05:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SUCKING THE CHARM POWER OUT
- Huh? What's all this?</font>

83
00:05:13,170 --> 00:05:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! It's Nissan!
Let's get a photo together!</font>

84
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a nice view, isn't it?</font>

85
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brought that on?</font>

86
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

87
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada-kun sent the
pictures from earlier.</font>

88
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. So many photos of
a bizarre group of people.</font>

89
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

90
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If not for the class trip energy,
we probably wouldn't have taken these.</font>

91
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, you had the chance.</font>

92
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've posed together.</font>

93
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

94
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could we take one with just us two?</font>

95
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With all those people
around, I just couldn't!</font>

96
00:05:57,250 --> 00:06:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just going up and talking to him used up
all my emotional strength for today.</font>

97
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">INCREDIBLE, NISSHI!
- You did work hard for that.</font>

98
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And actually...</i></font>

99
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yamada's got problems</i>
<i>without including me.</i></font>

100
00:06:07,790 --> 00:06:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He should've texted Nisshi privately.</i></font>

101
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Moron. Incompetent.</i></font>

102
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wasn't this a chance to contact her?</i></font>

103
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he texted again.
I wonder if it's a photo.</font>

104
00:06:22,290 --> 00:06:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of photo is it?</font>

105
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YAMADA
UNREAD MESSAGES BELOW
- CAN YOU LEAVE YOUR ROOM RIGHT NOW?</font>

106
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? He...
He's asking me directly. Wait.</font>

107
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When is "right now"? What do I do?</font>

108
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go, Nisshi.</font>

109
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But, Hon-chan,
I'd be leaving you alone.</font>

110
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a livestream I want to watch,
so I won't be bothered.</font>

111
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but...</font>

112
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'M IN THE LOBBY,
IN A PLACE WITH LOTS OF CHAIRS.</font>

113
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People are wandering around the</i>
<i>hotel a lot more than I thought.</i></font>

114
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's Yamada-kun.</i></font>

115
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, some girls</i>
<i>I don't know have arrived.</i></font>

116
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait. Does this mean that it's possible</i>
<i>I wasn't the only one he called out here?</i></font>

117
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, they left.</i></font>

118
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now here's someone else.</i></font>

119
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've only seen</i>
<i>that greeting done overseas.</i></font>

120
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, I feel like</i>
<i>Yamada-kun is with girls a lot.</i></font>

121
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's this?</i></font>

122
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>For some reason, I've naturally thought of</i>
<i>all of Yamada-kun's actions toward me</i></font>

123
00:07:25,210 --> 00:07:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as signs of some kind of affection,</i>
<i>and it turned my thinking into a mess.</i></font>

124
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what if this is all an</i>
<i>embarrassing misunderstanding?</i></font>

125
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like, for me this is something that never</i>
<i>happens, but for Yamada-kun it's normal?</i></font>

126
00:07:38,710 --> 00:07:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do? I have so little experience</i>
<i>that I never even thought to question it!</i></font>

127
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

128
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should say hi.</font>

129
00:07:48,580 --> 00:07:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um...</font>

130
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... you were
with other people, so...</font>

131
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. You don't want
other people to see you?</font>

132
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's, um...</font>

133
00:07:58,290 --> 00:08:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is bad.</i>
<i>My self-conscious side is showing.</i></font>

134
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you have a point.</font>

135
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, I hate the idea, too.</font>

136
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right now?</i></font>

137
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

138
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go and talk quietly
by ourselves.</font>

139
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All the awful imaginings</i>
<i>that were jumbled up in my head</i></font>

140
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>were blown away in an instant.</i></font>

141
00:08:30,290 --> 00:08:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yamada-kun's words and actions</i>
<i>are always so straightforward.</i></font>

142
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishi-san, was this cat around
when you went by?</font>

143
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No.</font>

144
00:08:42,130 --> 00:08:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cute!</font>

145
00:08:43,170 --> 00:08:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! This is Taira,
the guy I was telling you about...</font>

146
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I think I've seen him before.</font>

147
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this is Azuma...</font>

148
00:08:50,250 --> 00:08:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A pretty older sister.</font>

149
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this bald giant is Morimo.</font>

150
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">*MORIMOTO
- Morimo?</font>

151
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">TAIRA: OUR TURN FOR THE BATH IS COMING UP
- Oh.</font>

152
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gotta get back.</font>

153
00:08:58,830 --> 00:09:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, me too.</font>

154
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, um...</font>

155
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to go hang out somewhere?</font>

156
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the class trip.</font>

157
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, maybe somewhere we
won't run into anyone from school.</font>

158
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anywhere is good.</font>

159
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just the two of us.</font>

160
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

161
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

162
00:09:31,290 --> 00:09:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">WHY ME? WHAT SHOULD I ACCEPT? REALLY?
- <i>Thinking about Yamada-kun's feelings,</i>
<i>there's so much I don't understand.</i></font>

163
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate people who are evasive about
their true feelings, you know?</font>

164
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These feelings of mine...</i></font>

165
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't explain them away anymore.</i></font>

166
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love him.</font>

167
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MEANWHILE</font>

168
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing beats my bias.</font>

169
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back in middle school,</i>
<i>I couldn't say I didn't want to go,</i></font>

170
00:10:02,710 --> 00:10:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I reluctantly went,</i></font>

171
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>thinking "I want to hurry up and</i>
<i>go home" as I endured my class trip.</i></font>

172
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now...</i></font>

173
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to be honest...</i></font>

174
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm having fun. A lot of fun.</i></font>

175
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class trip, day three!</font>

176
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class activities!</font>

177
00:10:36,170 --> 00:10:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teacher! Is it okay for me
to get some ice cream?</font>

178
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How casual are you?</font>

179
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sure.</font>

180
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine?</font>

181
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, we got around to everything fast.</font>

182
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

183
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before I knew it, we had
left the other classes behind!</font>

184
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you make it back
before the bus leaves,</font>

185
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can wander around wherever.</font>

186
00:10:53,830 --> 00:10:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

187
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:56,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

188
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ya—</font>

189
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

190
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nothing.</font>

191
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop looking at me like that.</font>

192
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After breaking free of my hometown,</i></font>

193
00:11:08,250 --> 00:11:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may accidentally verge</i>
<i>on getting overly excited,</i></font>

194
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the moment I see myself</i>
<i>like that, my limiter kicks in.</i></font>

195
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">AZUMA KNOWS THE OLD ME.
BACK THEN, I WAS LOW-LEVEL, THOUGH.
- <i>Especially when I'm with Azuma.</i></font>

196
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I DON'T WANT HER THINKING I'M LIVING IT UP
IN THIS NEW ENVIRONMENT.
- <i>All these concerns mix together into...</i></font>

197
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An incomplete sense of
self-consciousness and inferiority.</font>

198
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where'd that come from?</font>

199
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Hey, I want to buy some deer senbei!</font>

200
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's ten in a packet. Shall we share?</font>

201
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

202
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

203
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

204
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, wanna go halfsies with me?</font>

205
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

206
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! They're already standing by!</font>

207
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're used to getting fed.</font>

208
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're really rushing over!</font>

209
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! This is pretty scary!</font>

210
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Drool! Calm down!</font>

211
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay! Stay! Time out! Stay!</font>

212
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay! Wait! Stay!</font>

213
00:11:57,790 --> 00:12:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada sure is talking
to those deer a lot.</font>

214
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen to this!</font>

215
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those deer ate everything they could
eat in a flash and then they all left!</font>

216
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't look like that's happening there.</font>

217
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have any more!</font>

218
00:12:10,210 --> 00:12:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira's so popular with the deer.</font>

219
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:16,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Stop laughing and help me!</font>

220
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

221
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BUS TOUR STYLE
- And now, if I could have your attention
for the return trip!</font>

222
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think we're gonna
keep this party going,</font>

223
00:12:36,210 --> 00:12:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">throw your hands in the air!</font>

224
00:12:37,710 --> 00:12:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

225
00:12:39,380 --> 00:12:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't give a mid-concert talk.</i></font>

226
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}In the front row! Tani-kun,
how's your car sickness?</font>

227
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop sliding personal info into your talk.</font>

228
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira.</font>

229
00:12:50,210 --> 00:12:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

230
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here.</font>

231
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YAMADA: HELPING WITH THE TALK,
TANI: MOVED, SUZUKI: GIVING THE TALK
- And now, I'd like to do a quiz!</font>

232
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's question 1!</font>

233
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What two animals are hidden
in the Japanese name for April 1st?</font>

234
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bought lots of snacks,
so let's eat some.</font>

235
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's way too many.</font>

236
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Those remind me of an elementary school
field trip. So nostalgic.
- Anyone know the answer?</font>

237
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Then it goes to you, Yamada!
- Nabe recommended them.</font>

238
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- No clue!
- Don't be so happy about it!
- You don't like Nabe-chan's picks, Taira?</font>

239
00:13:13,380 --> 00:13:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- The answer is, you take
the "itachi" from "shigatsu tsuitachi,"
- I wasn't complaining. Now sit properly.</font>

240
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Oh! Taira, this one has a lucky piece.
- and since that date is also referred to
as "watanuki," the answer is two tanuki!</font>

241
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you one.</font>

242
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me if you win, okay?</font>

243
00:13:22,290 --> 00:13:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

244
00:13:24,130 --> 00:13:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't understand it at all, did you?</font>

245
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's sour.</font>

246
00:13:29,290 --> 00:13:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Your reaction is way too small.
- And now for question 3!</font>

247
00:13:30,830 --> 00:13:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this normal? You expect weird stuff.
- What kind of bird do you get
when you have nine all together?</font>

248
00:13:37,830 --> 00:13:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here!</font>

249
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Zuma-chan! Having an active
participant is so helpful!</font>

250
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A nine-ah bird!</font>

251
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incorrect! Too bad!</font>

252
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And she got it wrong?</i></font>

253
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- What? But I was so sure it was right.
- That was a tough one.
The correct answer is... pigeon!</font>

254
00:13:49,670 --> 00:13:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why a pigeon?</font>

255
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Pigeon is written with kanji
for "nine" and "bird."
- You're weirded out because I was wrong?</font>

256
00:13:54,330 --> 00:13:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Yamada, can you write
the kanji for pigeon?
- Huh? No.</font>

257
00:13:55,920 --> 00:14:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- <i>It's just... Was Azuma always like this?</i>
- Pretty much no.
- Are you gonna be okay?</font>

258
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani, are you okay?</font>

259
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dinner tonight is all-you-can-eat!
Can you handle it?</font>

260
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meat! Meat! Meat!</font>

261
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make him imagine that right now!</font>

262
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to feel the wind
for a while. Go on ahead.</font>

263
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care!</font>

264
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't know
where to go, just call me!</font>

265
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

266
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And of course,
this is the one time I'm out of tea.</font>

267
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. Thank you.</font>

268
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You're having
a cola before a buffet?</font>

269
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to be that shocked.</font>

270
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's just... I've heard that
cola works for car sickness.</font>

271
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so kind of you!</font>

272
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop doing stuff like that!</font>

273
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, do you usually get carsick?</font>

274
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not usually. Just for some reason...</font>

275
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm all right now.</font>

276
00:14:57,710 --> 00:15:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a relief. Maybe you weren't
feeling well to begin with?</font>

277
00:15:01,710 --> 00:15:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still have tomorrow, too.</font>

278
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm all right.</font>

279
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, it gets chilly at night,
so I'll head back to where everyone—</font>

280
00:15:13,170 --> 00:15:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay with me just a little longer?</font>

281
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

282
00:15:36,210 --> 00:15:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?!
I regret ever worrying about him!</font>

283
00:15:42,330 --> 00:15:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was insane! They're totally living
the springtime of youth! I was shocked!</font>

284
00:15:46,830 --> 00:15:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw something great.
That was fun!</font>

285
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was not good and it was not fun!</font>

286
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I don't care anymore.
I'll drink this myself.</font>

287
00:15:57,540 --> 00:16:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Argh! Seriously?!</font>

288
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! I can't! My stomach hurts!</font>

289
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't laugh at other people's misfortune!</font>

290
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is something you laugh at.</font>

291
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow, Azuma, you're more...</font>

292
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">classmate-like than I thought.</font>

293
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Of course I am.</font>

294
00:16:32,130 --> 00:16:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

295
00:16:33,630 --> 00:16:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We always talk casually with each other.</font>

296
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we were in the same class
together last year, right?</font>

297
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

298
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I mean... That's true, but...</font>

299
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"You've changed somehow"</i>
<i>is what I wanted to, uh...</i></font>

300
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what good does saying that do?</i>
<i>That's creepy!</i></font>

301
00:16:51,170 --> 00:16:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

302
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What was that just now?</i></font>

303
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not fair!</i></font>

304
00:16:54,210 --> 00:16:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was adorable!</i></font>

305
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FEVERISH
RECOVERED A WHILE AGO</font>

306
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class trip, the final day!</font>

307
00:17:00,920 --> 00:17:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Free time!</font>

308
00:17:07,080 --> 00:17:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where should we go first?</font>

309
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have much time, though.</font>

310
00:17:11,290 --> 00:17:12,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you going somewhere else?</font>

311
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was blunt.</font>

312
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, enjoy your date.</font>

313
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we run into you,
we'll pretend we didn't.</font>

314
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. You don't have to go that far.</font>

315
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couples tend to argue on
amusement park dates, so be careful.</font>

316
00:17:25,170 --> 00:17:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go,
saying stuff like that again.</font>

317
00:17:27,330 --> 00:17:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When a guy has a bad attitude
waiting in lines or driving,</font>

318
00:17:31,380 --> 00:17:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should assume
that's their true nature.</font>

319
00:17:33,540 --> 00:17:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not from experience, is it?</font>

320
00:17:37,250 --> 00:17:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where do you want to start?</font>

321
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! There's a spot
I want to stop by first!</font>

322
00:17:41,330 --> 00:17:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it! A popcorn case!</font>

323
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to wear this
and walk around!</font>

324
00:17:46,710 --> 00:17:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it adorable?</font>

325
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adora...</font>

326
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like your thing.</font>

327
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to look at the hats
and headbands and stuff, too!</font>

328
00:17:57,580 --> 00:18:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is so exciting!</font>

329
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

330
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tani-kun, I wasn't expecting that choice.</i></font>

331
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This...</font>

332
00:18:10,290 --> 00:18:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">seems like you'd wear it.</font>

333
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd wear it?</i></font>

334
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean it'd look nice on me?</font>

335
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

336
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

337
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, which of these
would look good on Tani-kun?</font>

338
00:18:22,170 --> 00:18:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

339
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay without one.</font>

340
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

341
00:18:25,330 --> 00:18:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, really?</font>

342
00:18:28,290 --> 00:18:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was close! I was getting</i>
<i>all excited on my own again.</i></font>

343
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I don't get a grip,</i></font>

344
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he'll end up next to an avatar</i>
<i>loaded up with paid gacha pulls.</i></font>

345
00:18:37,170 --> 00:18:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But, I was sort of hoping to do casually</i>
<i>matching headbands or something.</i></font>

346
00:18:42,630 --> 00:18:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess he's not that type.</i></font>

347
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

348
00:18:46,710 --> 00:18:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to buy matching ones?</font>

349
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sort of... like we did before.</font>

350
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

351
00:18:56,960 --> 00:19:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Merch like this is okay,
but headbands are a no-go?</font>

352
00:19:00,170 --> 00:19:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... I can't imagine myself
wearing something like that.</font>

353
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They look good on you,
but I'd look weird, wouldn't I?</font>

354
00:19:07,710 --> 00:19:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You wouldn't look weird!</font>

355
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, in places like this,
you should be weird.</font>

356
00:19:13,670 --> 00:19:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll regret not going nuts.</font>

357
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

358
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's break out of that
shell of yours, Yuusuke-san!</font>

359
00:19:19,290 --> 00:19:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

360
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't like the idea!</font>

361
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine! No need to force yourself!</font>

362
00:19:29,630 --> 00:19:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want some? Go ahead.</font>

363
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

364
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For some reason, it's starting
to look cuter and cuter to me.</font>

365
00:19:41,630 --> 00:19:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it wasn't cute to you before?</font>

366
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is so much fun!</i></font>

367
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nabe and the others told me not to argue
because wait times are so long,</font>

368
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but not having fun is harder, right?</font>

369
00:20:08,330 --> 00:20:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEEDLESS WORRY OF THE YEAR</font>

370
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's true.</font>

371
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, time-wise, we might not
be able to do anything else.</font>

372
00:20:15,130 --> 00:20:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Already?</font>

373
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just got a text from Azu.</font>

374
00:20:22,210 --> 00:20:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like everyone else
is together.</font>

375
00:20:24,710 --> 00:20:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we should go and join them!</font>

376
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to get ready to
go home already? That's so sad!</font>

377
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miyu...</font>

378
00:20:43,210 --> 00:20:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...chan.</font>

379
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A BELATED "-CHAN"...</font>

380
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

381
00:20:49,290 --> 00:20:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

382
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's... take the long way there.</font>

383
00:20:57,790 --> 00:21:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yuusuke-kun... hold on.</font>

384
00:21:02,170 --> 00:21:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, you're...
Actually, yesterday, too...</font>

385
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, actually, before that, too...</font>

386
00:21:09,380 --> 00:21:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to kill me?</font>

387
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

388
00:21:13,210 --> 00:21:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know why. I...</font>

389
00:21:17,290 --> 00:21:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I've gone a little weird.</font>

390
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of laugh was that?</font>

391
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boys, that's crazy!</font>

392
00:21:29,580 --> 00:21:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you all wearing those?</font>

393
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd it start?</font>

394
00:21:32,290 --> 00:21:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the looks.</font>

395
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The crew members asked
about it, right?</font>

396
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize that people
greeted each other that much.</font>

397
00:21:39,170 --> 00:21:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}STARE...</font>

398
00:21:49,290 --> 00:21:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira-kun...</font>

399
00:21:50,630 --> 00:21:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">YOU'RE WEARING ONE...
- What? Why are you only
giving me that reaction?</font>

400
00:21:55,250 --> 00:21:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Let's all take
a group picture together!</font>

401
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

402
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you thinking you should've
just gone all the way insane?</font>

403
00:22:05,250 --> 00:22:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

404
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! I'm taking it now.</font>

405
00:22:08,290 --> 00:22:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a little.</font>

406
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

407
00:22:13,250 --> 00:22:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to come back, right?</font>

408
00:22:15,290 --> 00:22:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

